<!-- Letter Content -->
<main class="letter-content">
  <div class="letter-body">

    <p class="letter-greeting">Dear Maker,</p>

    <p class="letter-para">
      Code is becoming commodity. Your mojo isn't.
    </p>

    <p class="letter-para">
      What if you could go the extra mile for every customer? In four weeks, we'll capture how you work at your best and build an agent that scales it.
    </p>

    <p class="letter-para">
      We surface what you're too close to see and make it your competitive advantage.
    </p>

    <div class="letter-timeline">
      <div class="timeline-week">
        <span class="week-label">Week 1</span>
        <p>We extract what makes you special. Not your marketing copy. The real thing.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="timeline-week">
        <span class="week-label">Week 2</span>
        <p>We translate it into agentic behavior. The interface, the copy, the way it thinks.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="timeline-week">
        <span class="week-label">Week 3</span>
        <p>We make it sing. Prompts tuned, data wired up, systems humming.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="timeline-week">
        <span class="week-label">Week 4</span>
        <p>You take the wheel. We adjust until it delivers, then hand you the keys.</p>
      </div>

      <p class="timeline-footer">
        Next sprint available <strong class="start-date">October 6th</strong>. By <strong class="end-date">November 3rd</strong>, you'll have risen above the noise.
      </p>
    </div>

    <p class="letter-para">
      Worth a conversation?
    </p>

    <div class="letter-cta">
      <a href="#" class="cta-button-letter">Find a time</a>
      <p class="cta-alt">or reach out at <a href="mailto:hello@takuma.ai">hello@takuma.ai</a></p>
    </div>

    <div class="letter-signature">
      <p>— Kate + Neal</p>
      <p class="signature-sub">Takuma</p>
    </div>

  </div>
</main>

